Colossal 5–{8}{W}{W} [i](You may cast this for its colossal cost to have it enter with five +1/+1 counters; or pay {8}{W}{W} as a sorcery: Put five +1/+1 counters on it if it has none.)[/i]
Ward {5}
When Hekaton Dismantler’s colossal ability puts one or more counters on it, tap each creature you don’t control. Those creatures don’t untap during their controller’s next 100 untap steps.
